trans-unit.source: A collection of objects stored in session state.
trans-unit.target: En samling av objekter som er lagret i status for økten.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The SessionStateItemCollection class is used to manage session-state variable values indexed by a variable name or by numerical index.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SessionStateItemCollection brukes til å administrere økttilstanden variabelverdier indeksert ved et variabelnavn eller numerisk indeks.

trans-unit.source: The session-state variables are exposed to ASP.NET application code using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class, which is accessed using the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>.
trans-unit.target: Status for økten variablene er utsatt for ASP.NET-programmet kode ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>klassen som er tilgjengelig via <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A>egenskapen for den gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class calls the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> class, which manages session-state variable values using the SessionStateItemCollection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>klasse kall av <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer>klassen som administrerer status for økten variabelverdier ved hjelp av SessionStateItemCollection.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>

trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle verdier og nøkler fra samlingen status for økten.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"></xref> collection from a storage location that is written to using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*> method.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> samling fra en lagringsplassering som er skrevet til ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*>

trans-unit.source: The Deserialize method can be used to read the contents of a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> collection from the session store.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Deserialize kan brukes til å lese innholdet i en <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>samlingen fra økten store.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: To write the contents of a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> object to the session store, use the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Å skrive til innholdet i en <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>objekt økt-butikken, bruk av <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"></xref> collection populated with the contents from a storage location that is written to using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*> method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> samlingen fylt med innhold fra en lagringsplassering som er skrevet til ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Serialize*>

trans-unit.source: The session state information is invalid or corrupted
trans-unit.target: Informasjon om øktstatus er ugyldig eller skadet

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the collection has been marked as changed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om samlingen er merket som endret.

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is used to indicate whether the contents of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> collection have changed.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen endret brukes til å angi om innholdet i den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>samlingen er endret.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is set to `true` when an object value is set or added to the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A> property and when one or more object values are removed from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Skadet egenskapen er satt til `true` når en objektverdi som er angitt eller legges til i samlingen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>egenskapen og når én eller flere objektverdier fjernes fra samlingen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, eller <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is also set to `true` when a mutable object is retrieved from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen endret også er satt til `true` når en ruletemplatevariable objektet er hentet fra samlingen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: Calling the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A> method to populate a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> collection results in the Dirty property being set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Kaller den <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A>metode for å fylle ut et <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>samling, fører det endrede egenskapen er satt til `false`.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> innholdet har blitt endret; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
